Ti7 bou2 sou2-chai7 u7 chit8 e5 lang5 seN3 Bok8, mia5 Pi2-tek kap i e5 cha-bou2-kiaN2 Lo5-tai7 cho3-hoe2 khia7. Le2-pai3 e5-hng ti7 i e5 the-i2 teh che7, chiah8-chiu2 phoe3 hun, chiu7 ka7 Lo5-tai7 kong2, Lo5-tai7 ah! Bok8-su e7-pou sou2 kong2 e5 to7-li2 chin-chiaN3 si7 beng5, koh si7 oah8-tang7 e5 oe7, e7 kam2-kek lang5 e5 sim. Lo5-tai7 thiaN-liau2, mng7 in Pe7, khoaN3 sim2-mih8 bok8-su kong2 to7-li2. Pi2-tek in3 kong2, He2 si7 pat8-ui7 lai5-e5, goa2 m7-bat i.  Koh kong2, chin-chiaN3 si7 ho2 thiaN, lan2 ka-ti7 e5 bok8-su be7-hiau2 kong2 chit8 hun7-a2 chhin-chhiuN7 i an2-ni. Lo5-tai7 si7 ti3-sek e5 cha-bou2 gin2-na2 chai i-e5 pe7 kap Bok8-su u7 tam7-poh8 put-bok8, sou2-i2 u7 oan3-hin7 e5 oe7-i3, chai na7 kap i pian7-pok ia7 bo5 chhai2-kang cho3 an2-ni mng7, A-tia, I kong2 sim2-mih8 to7-li2. Pi2-tek kong2, I2-sek-liat8 lang5 teh koe3 Ang5-hai2 e5 su7. Te5-bak8 chiu7-si7 “I2-sek-liat8 lang5 kiaN5 ti7 hai2 tiong chhin-chhiuN7 kiaN5 ta-te7”. Thau5 chit8-hang7 kong2, Ang5-hai2 e7 pi2-pheng7 si7 lan2 sou2 khia7 e5 se3-kan, lan2 tioh8 kiaN5 koe3 chhin-chhiuN7 ti7 ta-te7, m7-thang hou7 se3-kan e5 choe7 bak-tioh8 lan2 e5 i-chiuN5 kap kha. Te7-ji7 hang7, Lan2 i2-keng tit-tioh8 Chu2 siok8-hoe5, lan2 tioh8 kiaN5 tiong-ng e5 lou7, m7-thang oa2 siang-peng5 im-si2 lang5 e5 choe7-kai3. Ai3-ah! Kong2 kau3 beng5-beng5 pek8-pek8; kong2 e5 tiong-kan bak8-chiu na2 khoaN3 I2-sek-liat8 lang5 teh koe3 Ang5-hai2 e5 khi2-siong7.  Lan2 e5 bok8-su na7 e7 hiau2 kong2 chhin-chhiuN7 i an2-ni chin-chiaN3 e7 kham-tit sng3-giah8.   
Koh2-sioh, Pi2-tek sou2 teh hin7 bok8-su chiu7-si7 an2-ni. Pi2-tek am3-si5 ai3 chiah8-chiu2, m7-na7 ka-ti7 ai3 chiah8 soa3 bian2-kiong2 i e5 cha-bou2-kiaN2 tioh8 kap i lim chit8 au-a2. Bok8-su tiaN7-tiaN7 khng3 i tioh8 kai3-chiu2 ka7 i kong2, chiah8-chiu2--e5 be7-tit thang jip8 Thian-tong5. Koh kong2, Li2 m7-na7 teh chou2-tong3 ka-ti7 soa3 teh be5 li2 e5 cha-bou2 gin2-na2. Pi2-tek siu7-khi3 ka7 bok8-su kong2, bo5 kan-siap8 li2 e5 tai7-chi3, chhut-chai7 goa2 chiah8! Na7 ai3 eng7 chiu2 se2 seng-khu ia7 thang. Bok8-su kong2, Li2 na7 eng7 chiu2 se2 seng-khu iau2-ku2 khah ti3-sek; se2 goa7-phoe5, ku2 be7 hai7-tioh8 sim-lai7. Pi2-tek koh khah siu7-khi3, tui3 an2-ni si3-koe3 chhoe7 khang3-khiah thang hiam5 bok8-su.   
Hit-e5-hng Pi2-tek na2-lim na2 o-lo2 pat8 ui7 lai5 e5 Bok8-su gau5 kong2 to7-li2; o-lo2 liau2 chiu7 soa3 khun3-khi3. Bang7 chit8 e5 bang7 khoaN3-kiN3 u7 hai2, siang-peng5 e5 chui2 koan5 kau3 na2 chhiuN5-piah, tiong-ng si7 ta e5 soa-lou7, soa kim sih-sih. Lou7 thau3 kau3 chit8 e5 siaN5. SiaN5-mng5, ke-lou7 tak8-ui7 choan-choan cheng-kim. Soa-lou7 teh ong2-lai5 e5 lang5 chin-che7, tak8-e5 ai3 jip8 siaN5-mng5. Soa-lou7 u7 thiN-sai3 eng7 kim-sau3-chhiu2 chhut-lat8 teh sau3-te3, ai3 chan7 koe3-lou7 e5 lang5 chheng-khi3 kau3 siaN5-mng5, hou7 kou3-mng5 e5 thang chun2 in jip8.   
U7-e5 chheng-khi3 chheng-khi3 kau3 mng5, kou3-mng5--e5 chiong thau5 kau3 kha siong5-se3 khoaN3, khoaN3 na7 bo5 chit8-tiam2 e5 la5-sam5, chin hoaN-hi2 khui-mng5 hou7 in jip8; lai7-bin7 lang5 ia7 hoaN-hoaN hi2-hi2 chiap-lap8 in. Iau2 u7-e5 bo5 se3-ji7, kiaN5-lou7 e5 si5 ai3 oa2 phian-piN hou7 hai2-chui2 phu3--tioh8 in e5 saN, kau3 siaN5-mng5 saN long2 chit8-jiah chit8-jiah e5 kiaN-lang5; kou3-mng5--e5 m7 ka7 in khui; in ka-ti7 iu-bun7, cho3 in tui3 pat8-ui7 khi3.   
