Pi2-tek chin siu7-khi3, mng7 ThiN-sai3 khoaN3, An2-choaN2 bo5 chou2-tong3 hit-e5 lang5. ThiN-sai3 io5-thau5 kong2, Kho2-sioh ah! goan2 e5 Chu2 m7-chun2 goan2 chhap i.   
Pi2-tek kong2, “M7 chun2”! Lin2 tioh8 ka-ti7 chu2-i3; hit-e5 lang5 m7-na7 teh hai7 ka-ti7 ia7 teh hai7 goa2 e5 kiaN2, tong3 i be7 jip8 hit-e5 eng5-kng e5 siaN5. Hai7 ah! Goa2-e5 kiaN2 ah! ThiN-sai3 kong2, Goa2 chai lah, kho2-sioh ah.   
Pi2-tek koh khah siu7-khi3 toa7-siaN jiang2, Kong2, Lin2 iau2-ku2 m7 khui-chhui3. ThiN-sai3 koh kong2, Goa2 bo5 hoat-tit. In ku2 m7 thiaN; tak8 lang5 si7 i ka-ti7 cho3 Chu2, chhut-chai7 li2 khng3-i, kau3-boe2 i chiu7 ka-ti7 chu2-i3; goan2 thiN-sai3 siuN7 long2 be7 chhut.   
Pi2-tek toa7 siu7-khi3 kong2, Li2 na7 m7, goa2 tek-khak beh tong3 i. ThiN-sai3 kong2, An2-ni e7 cho3-tit thiN-sai3 sou2 m7-thang cho3-e5, Siong7-te3 u7-si5 chun2 lang5 khi3 cho3.   
Pi2-tek tian2-seng3 hoat-lat8 kiaN5 kin7-oa2 hit-e5 phaiN2-sim e5 lang5 beh sak hou7 i to2; hong2-hut gong5-ngiah8 chit8-e7, koh khoaN3 khiok to7 si7 i pun2-sin. Chit-si5 tian-tian to3-to3, chui2-kan phah ka-lauh8, soa3 piN3 thou5-moe5; chheN2, khoaN3 m7 si7 kiaN-lang5-chui2, goan5 lai5 si7 chiu2! Lo5-tai7 kong2, A-tia ah, li2 u7 khi2-khun3 chhia-to2 chiu2-kan; chiu2 long2 bak-tioh8 thou5-kha e5 than2-a2.   
Pi2-tek iau2 poaN3-khun3, poaN3-chheN2, khoaN3 than2-a2 long2 tam5 kong2, U7-iaN2, khiu2 Lo5-tai7 e5 chhiu2 kah i kin2-kin2 khia7 pat8-ui7 kiaN-liau2 bak-tioh8 i e5 e5.    
